    &gt;Advent of Code&lt;/a&gt; with industrial control systems? Ladder logic solutions running on actual PLCs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This year, I solved Advent of Code 2025 puzzles using &lt;strong&gt;ladder logic on an Allen-Bradley Micro870 PLC&lt;/strong&gt;, with a FactoryTalk Optix HMI for visualization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Github Repo with Code: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/ladderlogix/Advent-of-Code-2025&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
